_aChangeLog.text: Changed most textures to fit in with rest of the map. It should be easier to spot enemies now because of brighter textures. With that I also increased quality of them making the map much prettier.
Portions of T side of the map have been changed and tweaked.
Added sounds to machines inside the A site.

_aLatestUpdates._sText: Regarding the improvement of T side of the map, I removed blacked out boxes that had lightning issues near A site and replaced them with an extended wall with plants on top, and I put a car as a hiding spot.

_sText: Map is set in desert-ish place, similar to Dust. It has a mix of mid and long range engagement places.
